Julian Richings https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julian_Richings 0 Julian M. Richings (born 8 September 1955) is an English-born Canadian actor. He has appeared in over 50 films and 20 television series. He is probably best known as Death in The CW's Supernatural.
